API Key will be generated automaticly ones activating intergation with ServiceNow. 

1 . go to Configuration > Third Party Integration > Application

2. In Application press the "+" option and choose "ServiceNow OT Visibility (CMDB) - SGC integration"

 

 

3. go to Configuration > User Managment > API KEYS 

4. press the eye button to see the API key created for ServiceNow integration
